    <detaileddescription>
<para>This weight is computed as <formula id="18">$w = 2 (\cot\beta + \cot\gamma)$</formula> with notations shown in the figure below.</para>
<para>Here, <computeroutput>q</computeroutput> is a query point and the points <computeroutput>p0</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>p1</computeroutput>, and <computeroutput>p2</computeroutput> are its neighbors.</para>
<para>Alternative formulations are explained in <ref refid="index_1Weights_Implementation" kindref="member">Implementation</ref>.</para>
<para><anchor id="group__PkgWeightsRefCotangentWeights_1fig__cotangent_weight"/> <image type="html" name="cotangent.svg"></image>
