</para>
<para><bold>Alternative Formulations</bold><linebreak/>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>This weight is equal to the <ref refid="group__PkgWeightsRefDiscreteHarmonicWeights" kindref="compound">Discrete Harmonic Weight</ref>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>This weight is a special case of the <ref refid="group__PkgWeightsRefThreePointFamilyWeights" kindref="compound">Three Point Family Weight</ref>.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
